{"id":"tarah","term":"Tarah","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Stopping; station, an encampment of the Hebrews in the wilderness (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 33:27\">Num. 33:27</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 33:28\">28</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Numbers 33:27","Numbers 33:28"]}